name: Enet
description:
Enet

Made For The Brackey's Game Jam Using P5, Aseprite, And SFXR

Controls:

Movement - WASD

Shoot - Mouse

Goal:

Hold Back The Enets Using Your Enet Cannon For As Long As You Can

(Tip Enemies Won't Appear To Die, When You Kill An Enemy Your Enet Bullet Becomes An Enet, If You Miss, It Will Become An Enet Without Killing Another One! Use Your Bullets Wisely)
